      "text": "God Medicine: Fantasy Sekai no Tanjou (ゴッドメディスン ファンタジー世界の誕生) is a role-playing video game released by Konami in 1993 for the Game Boy, only in Japan. An updated version of the game, God Medicine Fukkokuban (ゴッドメディスン復刻版), was re-released in 1998 through the Nintendo Power service, adding Super Game Boy support, a bestiary for encountered monsters and additional story elements.",
